item.title: Re: Possible Copy of this Wiki

item.title: Re: Possible Copy of this Wiki
item.content:encoded:
I've seen this a long time ago. It does not have all the pages and it is not up to date. I don't think anyone who has seen this wiki will be using it.

This is the work of Yoshirou. I don't know if he made it to raise his karma or just as a backup.
It does not appear on the first page when googling it so it does not hurt anyone.

item.title: Possible Copy of this Wiki
item.content:encoded:
Yo.

Looking around Google, I found a site called http://billysnakeman.wikidot.com/. It looks like it copied all the information from here and just pasted it onto their site. Their forum has the same topics that this wiki has, except no one's posted there. It doesn't look like it's run by anyone here.

I didn't know if this site was allowed or not, but I figured I'd post it here just in case they're doing something wrong.

Sorry for bothering ya if this isn't a big deal. It just looked slightly suspicious.
